%!PS

%	This example appears in section "Accurate Positioning"
%	in Chapter 4 - "Transformations".
%
%	Notes:		Replace x below with the appropriate value for your
%			device.

/inch { 72 mul } def			%  define inch procedure
4.25 inch 2 inch moveto			%  set current point
0 4.5 inch rlineto			%  add line segment
1 setlinewidth				%  one pixel line width
stroke					%  paint the path
showpage				%  display page
